overview.en: SWC is a ERC 20 token that follows a list of standards that they can be shared and exchanged for other tokens. Through digitalization, it gives token holders potential portability and access of a digital wallet.  It has complete anonymity and measures of proof of interest (POS). SWC will be able to support other “tokens” that can represent a currency, shares, or any tangible physical assets. SWC will go through a periodic Proof of Burn that is available for both miners and developers.
overview.zh: SWC是ERC 20的数字资产，遵循一系列可以共享和交换的其他数字资产的标准。 通过数字化，它使该持有者具有潜在的便携性和数字钱包的访问权限。 它具有完全的匿名性和权益证明措施（POS）。 SWC将能够支持其他代表数字资产，股票或任何有形资产。 SWC将定期进行销毁证明（POB），矿工和开发商均可使用。
